&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Summary&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a Kong API Gateway Specialist to support the federal government in modernizing and securing enterprise APIs across mission-critical tax systems. The candidate will design, implement, and maintain Kong solutions that align with federal compliance mandates, enable developer experience, and support high-volume API traffic during filing season.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, configure, and maintain Kong API Gateway (Enterprise and OSS) for enterprise services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement plugins for authentication, authorization, rate limiting, caching, logging, and transformation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Integrate Kong with IAM and Zero Trust initiatives, including support for OAuth2, OpenID Connect, and mutual TLS.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop automation for Kong configurations using decK, Terraform, or Ansible.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure compliance with federal security standards, FISMA, FedRAMP, and NIST 800-53 controls.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor and optimize API performance using Prometheus, Grafana, and Splunk dashboards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support DevOps pipelines for API deployment across test, staging, and production environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with developers, system integrators, and operations staff to ensure seamless API delivery and support code freeze requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop documentation, standard operating procedures, and training materials for the staff.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years in API management, integration, or middleware, with 2+ years in Kong Gateway administration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in federal environments (IRS, Treasury, DHS, etc.) strongly preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on expertise with Kong Enterprise, decK, hybrid and DB-less modes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of containerization and orchestration (Docker, Kubernetes, OpenShift).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong scripting skills (Python, Lua, Shell).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with federal-scale observability tools (Prometheus, Grafana, Splunk).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience in secure API deployments and Zero Trust architecture.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
